Zoe blinked. &quot;Yes. What is funny?&quot;
&quot;Nothing,&quot; Grover said, trying to keep a straight face. &quot;I could use some dam french fries.&quot;
Even Thalia smiled at that. &quot;And I need to use the dam restroom.&quot;
